commit.message:
NumPy's tostring -> tobytes warning (Python 3.8 stops suppressing deprecation warnings) (#514)

* Update cursor.py

Removed deprecated use of tostring() method in python version >= 3.8. Using tobytes() method instead

* Update TTree.py

Removed deprecated use of tostring() method for python version >= 3.8. Using tobytes method instead

* Update TTree.py

* Update cursor.py

* Use 'tobytes' on NumPy arrays if it exists; 'tostring' if it doesn't.

Co-authored-by: Jim Pivarski <jpivarski@gmail.com>
